{"tid":1403671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【85戰術】大家估下班狗最唔想邊到發生衝突?","createTime":"2019-08-03T20:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:14.000Z","uid":214177,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b365b3ef3c7f40de43f9da7d19057a224de611","tid":1403671,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:35:12.000Z","msg":"兩個月大大小小嘅街頭抗爭 戰術終於成形<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">班狗既軟肋就係民居</span></strong><br />\n每一次去到民居 街坊們都係MVP 一呼百應<br />\n的確 畀著你見到有班狗踩上自己地頭 相信每個人都會理直氣壯咁屌走佢<br />\n<br />\n另一原因 地區戰會對狗造成既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">精神打擊較大</span></strong><br />\n其一係be water戰術容易執行 班狗會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">疲於奔命</span></strong><br />\n其二 化身為街坊既各位更有效<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">揭開班狗既遮醜布</span></strong><br />\n「黃大仙唔歡迎你」<br />\n「呢到私人地方，躝啦黑警」<br />\n<br />\n西環、旺角街頭戰嘅好處係容易集火<br />\n但同時亦都容易一野被吹熄 <br />\n當大街兩邊拉哂閘 黑警戴哂狗罩 成條街就淨返低一堆黑衫嘅目標<br />\n728當晚大家食彈食得咁辛苦 就係因為班狗可以肆無忌憚咁放煙<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位手足 8月5日 全港罷工 七區集會<br />\n連日抗爭我哋一係慘敗 一係慘勝<br />\n各位街坊 今次要大勝<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93SpSkE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93SpSkE.png&h=cfbfb267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c4ac2654fde1e610dcb4b6ec3e94423d34e9c6d","tid":1403671,"uid":28831,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:39:17.000Z","msg":"宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7區宿舍都有示威者唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2469cc0e1595e99366ad410b56ed39c66a7f06e6","tid":1403671,"uid":214177,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:40:39.000Z","msg":"正如5年前一樣<br />\n政府一路都冷處理緊呢場運動<br />\n我知你知 林奠都知你知<br />\n但係7婆估唔到 今次班癲狗係變數<br />\n佢地不受控既行為 成為維持呢場運動既燃料"},{"pid":"c520e2483b8c7e7e237b769e692e0fc191f53214","tid":1403671,"uid":59989,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:41:18.000Z","msg":"搞宿舍 <br />\n有哂妻兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07e498999fd029b134f7b39f77796e9cb66cc4a","tid":1403671,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:44:51.000Z","msg":"來荃灣"},{"pid":"91f85f7925088f19c5caf3cf0d88e9ffaf88783a","tid":1403671,"uid":214177,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:51:07.000Z","msg":"半個月前 <br />\n我開過一個post講中聯辦點樣滲透輿論 點樣控制風向<br />\n感激大家一路都幫推<br />\n縱觀連登情況 整場運動嘅焦點已經冇當初咁清晰<br />\n無論係言論受到控制又好 局勢變得複雜又好 <br />\n唔該大家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只推有用post</span></strong><br />\n記唔記得69 612前<br />\n成個時事台都係戰術post 行動post 文宣post 打氣post <br />\n各位 頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841a19aafe03363ac48863b02b0f3c769cf29ab9","tid":1403671,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:55:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4adb075ffc304f17d8c79151b04b91f40663d5e","tid":1403671,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:57:14.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"0edece8e35274d70bd4b5247b6c29f6a7923cc8c","tid":1403671,"uid":214177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9154f7ae762381050ad80acfe82a174c37560a76","tid":1403671,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:14:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4cb23226aaebc9a